An Interview with The Bones of J.R. Jones ... Meet vocalist, guitarist, and songwriter, Jonathon Linaberry. His newest album, “One to Keep Close” is out May 11th.
The Bones of JR Jones is a project from American singer, guitarist, and songwriter Jonathon Linaberry (born in central New York State in 1982).
